<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause"?><clause id="_64bb0a3a-fbb6-4654-bd5e-29f493d77d6b" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="TAS"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>I13D6</sptc><title id="_070bf0f1-a5e6-4910-8ed0-06d7cdc12a3c">Required exits</title><archive-num>2019: TAS H115.6</archive-num><subclause id="_2b416e89-7212-43f1-8e69-9c04ddf9f9b8" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_029fc59f-b818-47cc-b321-745e5c66f27c">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Every building and divisional area of a work place must have not less than 2 <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_a821a113-5764-4e20-ad65-865430d4dbc8" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exits</xref> for escape purposes.</p></subclause><subclause id="_e88f50b9-35a9-4132-aa7a-a6f4732a3f86" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_7afeccee-c3c0-41c4-9404-93d99a5d15a4">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The number and location of the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_6bee9186-15bd-44c8-9555-e4d9175f54b0" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exits</xref> must be such that any point on the floor is not more than 20 m from one of the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_de8c8b49-963d-4f9d-ab43-7170b3542209" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exits</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_99127fac-66a7-4c44-bc66-7c8495f9596f" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_4fbae1cd-39ca-4ad5-9eb5-86bb0f03ad1c">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>Only <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_52ac6899-4c5e-4b2f-a687-b649acb3a912" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exits</xref> with vertically hinged swinging doors may be considered as <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_d14c50b3-1c5a-46ae-bf79-0fa2f3ddbf88" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exits</xref> for the purposes of this clause.</p></subclause></clause>